casebody.data:
FLORIDA, plaintiff,
v.
GEORGIA. No. 142, Original. Supreme Court of the United States Feb. 21, 2017.

Motion of the Special Master for allowance of fees and disbursements is granted, and the Special Master is awarded a total of $213,547.35 for the period September 1, 2016, through December 31, 2016, to be paid equally by the parties.
